          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1671534135255-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1671534135255-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1671534135255-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1671534151383-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1671534151383-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1671534151383-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1671534151383-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1671534151383-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stew has been in the oven for 25 min, chop your<strong> tortillas</strong> into quarters (keep them stacked for speedy chopping!)</p><p>Add the <strong>tortilla quarters</strong> to a baking tray (or two) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through and lightly golden around the edges</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1671534164017-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1671534164017-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1671534164017-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1671534164017-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1671534164017-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced butternut squash & pepper stew </strong>with the <strong>crispy tortillas </strong>and <strong>soured cream </strong>to the side</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>roughly over the soured cream with scissors</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
